Tight integration for mvapich-1 was tested with version
mvapich-1.1-r5233.

Building mvapich
================
When you build mvapich, make sure to configure with option -rsh=rsh.

Installing the PE
=================
qconf -Ap $SGE_ROOT/mpi/mvapich/mvapich.template
